WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.020 --> 00:00:10.020
 250 gr. flour, 125 gr. soft butter, 125 gr. sugar powder, 1 large egg, 30 gr. black chocolate, 10 gr. cocoa, 2 gr. baking powder, 1 topped knife with salt, vanilla essence and 2 tablespoons of milk (optional). 

00:00:10.020 --> 00:00:14.060
 Mix butter and sugar until we get a homogeneous cream. 

00:00:38.580 --> 00:01:05.400
 Add egg, salt, vanilla and mix well. 

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:57.420
 Add melted chocolate to bain-marie (after melting leave a few minutes to cool). Stir until homogeneous. 

00:02:42.620 --> 00:02:55.960
 Mix the flour with the cocoa and the baking powder and grind them through a very thick sieve. Add the mixture in the dough and mix until it is homogenized. 

00:03:10.220 --> 00:03:18.360
 If the dough is too dense, add 1-3 tablespoons of milk and stir. 

00:04:28.080 --> 00:04:38.800
 Bake cooked in the preheated oven for 13-15 minutes. 

00:04:45.780 --> 00:04:50.120
 Let them cool in the tray, then decorate them with chocolate that was temperate and almonds / hazelnuts / nuts (according to your preference). 

